{"tid":933191,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"LoveLive! 新街機發生「全員裸體」BUG，遊戲瞬間變18禁 ","createTime":"2018-12-08T11:01:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T11:47:53.000Z","uid":199590,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7ce73c85903bee0d12bbeb08edd9f80e5eabc390","tid":933191,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T11:01:14.000Z","msg":"日本知名偶像音樂遊戲《LoveLive!》（ラブライブ）於今（6）日在日本全國推出新機台「スクフェス AC Next Stage」，令許多粉絲興奮不已，不過顯然工程師給玩家們開了個大玩笑，因為目前許多遊戲機台發生嚴重 BUG，導致&nbsp;Aqours 全部團員都是「裸體」登場...<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n沒錯，一個 BUG 就讓《LoveLive!》變成 18 禁遊戲。「スクフェス AC Next Stage」因不明原因，導致玩家在遊戲中所看到的舞蹈畫面，全部團員都呈現沒穿任何服裝的「裸體」畫面。雖說是裸體，其實不過是&nbsp;3D 模組的素體而已，但依然讓玩家感到尷尬與害羞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/37292/a-embarrassing-bug-making-lovelive-aracde-model-becoming-nude\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F37292%2Fa-embarrassing-bug-making-lovelive-aracde-model-becoming-nude&d=z3BjxEhhvHs7ZcFl%2BLMB3ozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=a1ea915c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/37292/a-embarrassing-bug-making-lovelive-aracde-model-becoming-nude</a>"},{"pid":"6dc178dccdebd95acabce8d18d567f8f61ccc071","tid":933191,"uid":100150,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T11:01:41.000Z","msg":"No photo no talk"},{"pid":"3444730d1ae67e64aaabec36e68a00f81880771a","tid":933191,"uid":199590,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6dc178dccdebd95acabce8d18d567f8f61ccc071","tid":933191,"uid":100150,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T11:01:41.000Z","msg":"No photo no talk"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T11:02:56.000Z","msg":"link都俾埋你 仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea8db853917ed5b46d66caa8e200a0e09a0a447","tid":933191,"uid":45232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T11:02:59.000Z","msg":"咁先係做生意嫁麻"},{"pid